<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Patch>
  <Operation Class="PatchOperationFindMod">
    <mods>
      <li>Vanilla Plants Expanded</li>
    </mods>
    <match Class="PatchOperationSequence">
      <success>Always</success>
      <operations>
        <li Class="PatchOperationReplace">
          <success>Always</success>
          <xpath>/Defs/ThingDef[defName="VCE_UncookedBorscht"]/label</xpath>
          <value>
            <label>생 보르시치</label>
          </value>
        </li>
        <li Class="PatchOperationReplace">
          <success>Always</success>
          <xpath>/Defs/ThingDef[defName="VCE_UncookedBorscht"]/description</xpath>
          <value>
            <description>전통적인 비트 수프입니다. 먹을 수 있도록 전기 냄비에서 조리해야 합니다.</description>
          </value>
        </li>
        <li Class="PatchOperationReplace">
          <success>Always</success>
          <xpath>/Defs/ThingDef[defName="VCE_Borscht"]/label</xpath>
          <value>
            <label>축제 보르시치</label>
          </value>
        </li>
        <li Class="PatchOperationReplace">
          <success>Always</success>
          <xpath>/Defs/ThingDef[defName="VCE_Borscht"]/description</xpath>
          <value>
            <description>비트로 천천히 끓인 수프입니다. 겨울에 먹으면 모두에게 축제의 기쁨을 채워 주며, 축제의 호의를 부여합니다.</description>
          </value>
        </li>
        <li Class="PatchOperationReplace">
          <success>Always</success>
          <xpath>/Defs/RecipeDef[defName="VCE_CookBorscht"]/label</xpath>
          <value>
            <label>보르시치 준비하기</label>
          </value>
        </li>
        <li Class="PatchOperationReplace">
          <success>Always</success>
          <xpath>/Defs/RecipeDef[defName="VCE_CookBorscht"]/description</xpath>
          <value>
            <description>비트를 사용해 전통적인 생 보르시치를 준비하세요.</description>
          </value>
        </li>
        <li Class="PatchOperationReplace">
          <success>Always</success>
          <xpath>/Defs/RecipeDef[defName="VCE_CookBorscht"]/jobString</xpath>
          <value>
            <jobString>보르시치 준비하는 중.</jobString>
          </value>
        </li>
      </operations>
    </match>
  </Operation>
</Patch>